# Группа Пользователи

## Пользователь [/users/{id}]

+ Parameters
    + id (integer) - ID пользователя

### Получить пользователя [GET]

+ Headers

        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "username": "john_doe",
            "name": "John Doe",
            "email": "john@example.com",
            "type_id": 1
        }

### Обновить пользователя [PUT]

+ Headers

        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "john_doe",
            "name": "John Doe",
            "email": "john@example.com",
            "type_id": 1
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "User updated"
        }

+ Response 403 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Forbidden - can only update own profile"
        }

### Удалить пользователя [DELETE]

+ Headers

        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "User deleted"
        }

+ Response 403 (application/json)

        {
            "message": "Forbidden - insufficient permissions"
        }

## Коллекция пользователей [/users]

### Создать пользователя [POST]

+ Headers

        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "john_doe",
            "name": "John Doe",
            "password_hash": "hashed_password",
            "email": "john@example.com",
            "type_id": 1
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "message": "User created"
        }

### Получить всех пользователей [GET]

+ Headers

        Authorization: Bearer {token}

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "username": "john_doe",
                "name": "John Doe",
                "email": "john@example.com",
                "type_id": 1
            }
        ]

